{
  "stem": "3659.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And by that time, I had already escalated to being a full-time operator, and I was making a few more dollars a week.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everything was always piecework.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You worked piecework.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was the time when the unions started to become very strong, and I--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was 15, but I told them I was 17, because otherwise I couldn't have gotten an Social Security card.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a very low number in Social Security.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- the Social Security.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, I was 15 at the time when I was working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was brutally hot in New York, and little, you know, young girls, they just passed out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you couldn't stop working, because if you stopped working you didn't make money, so you couldn't feed your family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my sister and I always said, Mama will not go to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We won't let her go to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We'll provide somehow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So between her working as a nursemaid, I was working in the sweatshop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then at night I came home, and we took in homework, and we stuffed little animals, piecework, and we did that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I knitted on the weekends-- I'm-- I was knitting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Somehow we survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We ate bread.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother used to go, with gloves on, to the-- to the grocery store and she said, do you happen to have any fruit that may be a little bit tainted that I can buy cheaply?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, lady, whatever you want, just go pick the fruit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You don't have to pay me anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she used to go there, very elegant, you know, nice, and bring home the fruit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all we did was cut off the-- the bad spot, and we made compotes out of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
